  <compounddef id="COLOUR" kind="page">
    <compoundname>COLOUR</compoundname>
    <title>COLOUR / COLOR Keyword</title>
    <briefdescription>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para><programlisting filename=".basic"><codeline><highlight class="normal">COLOUR<sp/>integer-expression</highlight></codeline>
</programlisting></para>
<para>Sets the <bold>text foreground colour</bold> to a VGA palette entry (0â€“15). <linebreak/>
 The default terminal colour is <bold>7</bold> (white).</para>
<para><image type="html" name="https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/1556794/234695075-9097ef8c-6d94-4736-ab62-bfdbc7696f0c.png" alt="VGA background and foreground colour chart" inline="yes"></image>
</para>
<para><blockquote><para>Both British and American spellings are accepted: <computeroutput>COLOUR</computeroutput> and <computeroutput>COLOR</computeroutput>. </para>
</blockquote></para>
<sect2 id="COLOUR_1autotoc_md208">
<title>&lt;/blockquote&gt;</title>
<para><heading level="5">Example</heading>
</para>
<para><programlisting filename=".basic"><codeline><highlight class="normal">COLOUR<sp/>14</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">PRINT<sp/>&quot;This<sp/>text<sp/>is<sp/>bright<sp/>yellow.&quot;</highlight></codeline>
</programlisting></para>
<para><hruler/>
</para>
