<para><hruler/>
</para>
<para><heading level="5">Notes</heading>
</para>
<para><itemizedlist>
<listitem><para>Applies to <bold>text output</bold> (e.g., <computeroutput>PRINT</computeroutput>). <linebreak/>
</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>The setting affects subsequent text until changed again. <linebreak/>
</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>For <bold>background</bold> colour, use <ulink url="https://github.com/brainboxdotcc/retro-rocket/wiki/BACKGROUND"><computeroutput>BACKGROUND</computeroutput></ulink>. <linebreak/>
</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>For <bold>graphics drawing colours</bold>, use <ulink url="https://github.com/brainboxdotcc/retro-rocket/wiki/GCOL"><computeroutput>GCOL</computeroutput></ulink>.</para>
</listitem></itemizedlist>
</para>
<para><bold>See also:</bold> <ulink url="https://github.com/brainboxdotcc/retro-rocket/wiki/BACKGROUND"><computeroutput>BACKGROUND</computeroutput></ulink>, <ulink url="https://github.com/brainboxdotcc/retro-rocket/wiki/GCOL"><computeroutput>GCOL</computeroutput></ulink> </para>
</sect2>
